Articles.Content:
My first rover to discover traces of water on duna, My first rover to have a hipster looking camera mast, My first rover to have cool looking science stuff on board, My first rover to land using landing legs.

This is also the rover that taught me something pretty interesting, turns out Ike is in a geosynchronous orbit, never knew that...

Reply with what you think, I might put up a download link for the rover and landing stages.
post up plans! i would like to check this out first hand. looks great! good job mate!
